<Base>
    <h1>About me</h1>

    <div class="container">
        <img src="/sphere.gif" alt="cat spinning in a sphere" style="float:left;" />

        <p>
            Hey! My name is Davi, but you can call me <b>argon</b> or
            <b>argonptg</b>. I am a second-year high school student and have experience in <b>Javascript</b>, <b>Typescript</b>, and <b>Svelte</b>, and I'm currently learning <b>C#</b> in technical school.
            On a daily basis, I use Arch Linux.
        </p>
        <p>
            Changing the subject, I am passionate about sports, especially Formula 1 and Soccer.
            In F1, I root for <b>McLaren</b> and for <b>Bortoleto</b>
            <i>(which has been impressing quite a few people)</i>. In football, I’ve been an <b>Atleticano</b> since birth and also support <b>Nottingham Forest</b>.
            I also can’t forget about PTCG, where I play and (try to) be good.
        </p>

        <p>
            Besides, this site is just a corner for me to post things I like and that interest me;
            I hope that you <em>(yes, you reading this)</em> have enjoyed this site!
            Below are some buttons and webrings that I like/participate in.
        </p>
    </div>

